overview: Don Ángel lives in retirement, showing films to the children of his glorious era as a wrestler, when he was known as EL FANTÁSTICO. A mysterious NAHUAL "the spirit of a person who is credited with magical powers obtained by the devil" has terrified the people of the town, the legend of EL FANTÁSTICO will resurface to face that curse.
title: El Fantástico vs. el nahual
